text: Baramee Limwattana (, born January 4, 1996), is a Thai professional footballer. ==Personal life== Baramee has a brother Sansern Limwattana is also a footballer and plays for Bangkok United as a Midfielder. ==Honours== ===Club=== ;Chainat Hornbill * Thai League 2 (1); 2017 ==References== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:People from Samut Prakan Province Category:Thai footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Waitakere United players Category:Thawiwatthana F.C. players Category:Buriram United F.C. players Category:New Zealand Football Championship players Category:Thai League 1 players Category:Thai League 2 players Category:Thai expatriate footballers Category:Thai expatriate sportspeople in New Zealand Category:Expatriate association footballers in New Zealand
